title: Sparkle [LOGIC / PUZZLE GAME]
description:
Zuma Sparkle

Use your puzzle skills to free the Crowberry Woods from the shadow of Darkness in this exciting action-puzzler. Use your Orb Slinger to shoot colored spheres into groups of three or more and reclaim every corner of this once vibrant forest. Discover amazing amulets and glittering power-ups hidden along the shaded path. Featuring three game modes and loads of intriguing levels, Sparkle is fast, colorful, and full of addictive fun!
